{"tid":2180860,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"因蠔涌爆炸品案坐牢 瘦仔變健碩 獄中健身自強 釋囚組過來人教練團","createTime":"2020-08-30T07:43:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T08:00:30.000Z","uid":301666,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a5dfdec688976312a584854dafb8aef6fc778199","tid":2180860,"uid":301666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T07:43:08.000Z","msg":"靚仔手足IG:<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/rizzy_bodycraft?igshid=1ginq6wn6a2w3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Frizzy_bodycraft%3Figshid%3D1ginq6wn6a2w3&d=XjGeTWWNN7bjI%2BfZ7PvsLPZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=a444bcfb\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/rizzy_bodycraft?igshid=1ginq6wn6a2w3</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】阿烈雙手按着地板，用力一撐，世界立時顛倒過來，雙腿倚傍牆壁借力，這是他在獄中最喜歡的時刻。2015年時21歲的彭艾烈（Rizzy Pennelli）捲入「蠔涌爆炸品案」，串謀製造炸藥和管有炸藥罪成，被判監3年10個月。原本囚禁他的監獄，卻成為他的健身室，他出獄後成為健身教練，希望組成一個「有故事的人」的團隊，在全港各區公園推廣健身，「我想自己係一個sample（樣辦），坐監出嚟都做到教練，我想做一個坐監嘅人嘅燈塔，畀人見到有人都做到，佢自己都做到」，無奈第三波疫情來襲，計劃需暫時擱置。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/港聞/article/20200830/s00002/1598724703467/【周日人物】因蠔涌爆炸品案坐牢-瘦仔變健碩-獄中健身自強-釋囚組過來人教練團\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200830%2Fs00002%2F1598724703467%2F%E3%80%90%E5%91%A8%E6%97%A5%E4%BA%BA%E7%89%A9%E3%80%91%E5%9B%A0%E8%A0%94%E6%B6%8C%E7%88%86%E7%82%B8%E5%93%81%E6%A1%88%E5%9D%90%E7%89%A2-%E7%98%A6%E4%BB%94%E8%AE%8A%E5%81%A5%E7%A2%A9-%E7%8D%84%E4%B8%AD%E5%81%A5%E8%BA%AB%E8%87%AA%E5%BC%B7-%E9%87%8B%E5%9B%9A%E7%B5%84%E9%81%8E%E4%BE%86%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%99%E7%B7%B4%E5%9C%98&d=XjGeTWWNN7bjI%2BfZ7PvsLPZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=7eb55d8b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200830%2Fs00002%2F1598724703467%2F%E3%80%90%E5%91%A8%E6%97%A5%E4%BA%BA%E7%89%A9%E3%80%91%E5%9B%A0%E8%A0%94%E6%B6%8C%E7%88%86%E7%82%B8%E5%93%81%E6%A1%88%E5%9D%90%E7%89%A2-%E7%98%A6%E4%BB%94%E8%AE%8A%E5%81%A5%E7%A2%A9-%E7%8D%84%E4%B8%AD%E5%81%A5%E8%BA%AB%E8%87%AA%E5%BC%B7-%E9%87%8B%E5%9B%9A%E7%B5%84%E9%81%8E%E4%BE%86%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%99%E7%B7%B4%E5%9C%98&h=2be8d95e\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/港聞/article/20200830/s00002/1598724703467/【周日人物】因蠔涌爆炸品案坐牢-瘦仔變健碩-獄中健身自強-釋囚組過來人教練團</a>"},{"pid":"de0e5ef39eef879bb3efa1069877d19a048e74f4","tid":2180860,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T07:43:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d8929b3baddbc9ef0b20ecae951051f3bf8f317","tid":2180860,"uid":255789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T07:51:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"199ebe5fb699f25cfa40f9ea28126be53d892b2a","tid":2180860,"uid":121546,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T07:53:19.000Z","msg":"真&middot;囚徒健身<br />\n有囚徒/土炮軍火就更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07aba39db5600fbf5c993eeab4bc656f01fc536b","tid":2180860,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T07:54:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"454ad4ecf6418cbd0b4a44e8dd61a7f9